data.description: 3 bed/2bath House with attached guest house in desirable Croissant Park (4/3 total). Perfect for airbnb, roommates, entertaining, and more! Close to Everything Ft Lauderdale has to offer. Easy access to 95, Airport, Beaches, 5 mins to Downtown/Las Olas, Lauderdale Marine Center, Broward Hospital, and Port Everglades. Spacious open floor plan, light & bright with BRAND NEW 2023 impact windows, Large back yard with deck just off the Main house kitchen, Master Suite with 2 closets, Florida Room, Separate Laundry room, title floors all throughout. Guest house is a studio, separate private entrance, full kitchen, laundry, and screened in porch. 2018 ROOF
